[](javascript:scrollToTop();) Ginkgo Biloba Ginkgo biloba has been used in Chinese medicine for thousands of years. It helps maintain normal blood flow to the brain, which is particularly important in old age. It also helps to maintain healthy circulation to the body's extremities.
